## Overview
Wire up the 4-screen inspection flow to a FastAPI backend using your **existing** AWS PostgreSQL tables (`templates`, `checklist_items`, `inspections`, `inspection_answers`).  
The current backend is using a different table set (`checklists`, `checklist_questions`). We will **not** touch those â€” we'll write new FastAPI endpoints that target your actual production tables.

