### Backend â€” New Router & Schemas

#### [NEW] `backend/app/api/v1/endpoints/templates.py`
New FastAPI router for templates CRUD:
- `GET /templates` â€” list all templates
- `POST /templates` â€” create template (`name`, `work_type`)  â†’ returns `template_id`
- `GET /templates/{id}/items` â€” get checklist_items for a template
- `POST /templates/{id}/items` â€” add a checklist_item to a template

#### [NEW] `backend/app/api/v1/endpoints/inspections_v2.py`
New FastAPI router for inspections (new tables only):
- `GET /inspections-v2` â€” list inspections
- `POST /inspections-v2` â€” create inspection (`template_id`, `project_name`, `assigned_to`, `due_date`)  â†’ returns `inspection_id`
- `GET /inspections-v2/{id}/items` â€” join `inspections` + `checklist_items` via `template_id`
- `POST /inspections-v2/{id}/answers` â€” upsert into `inspection_answers`

